subSections.text: {{ja-forms|芸 [[蕓]] 芸|芸 芸 [[艺]]|芸 [[蕓]] [[藝]]}} <!-- duplication to indicate which traditional characters correspond to which simplified characters -->

subSections.title: Usage notes
subSections.text: This character was originally derived from [[蕓]], and is also used to simplify it in Traditional Chinese; in Japanese, it is the simplified form of [[藝]], which was simplified differently in Chinese.
